# applications.fpga.system-example-designs.agilex5-ed-pcie-rp
#
#The SED PCie Rootport is a system level application to showcase Altera IPs.
#This folder contains Design, Verification, Build/Synthesis files for deloping this system design
#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

##### README file - Steps to simulate SM (Sundance Mesa) System-Example-Design PCIe Rootport ##### 

   1. To clone a fresh repository (this step need to do once for new repo)
      % git clone git clone https://github.com/intel-innersource/applications.fpga.system-example-designs.agilex5-ed-pcie-rp.git <myclone_name>

   2. Makefile: Get resource, compile, and run simulation
      Please see README file under <RP_ROOTDIR>/verification/scripts/sm_4x4 directory for steps to get resources and run simulation

   3. ITF: Get resource, compile, and run simulatiom
      Please see README file under <RP_ROOTDIR>/verification/script/itf directory for steps to get resources and run simulation

